{"tid":1627717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手推比文宣巴絲] 資訊戰既走向","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T17:33:34.000Z","uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d8c226735c34490e11136d174887e17d77a761","tid":1627717,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"話說小弟岩岩睇完白兵既資訊戰片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j9ueruIUEqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj9ueruIUEqQ&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpAFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=9c973279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j9ueruIUEqQ</a><br />\n白兵係入面講左要係一個政治運動既資訊戰取得勝利係有四個要點<br />\n<br />\n成功的政治運動有四大原則.<br />\n一、訊息規範: 將核心訊息用明確、簡易、容易理解不斷重覆, 訊息最重要是可以將情感傳遞<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">EG︰口號: 721唔見人 831打死人 -&gt; 明確,簡易地向警察帶出不滿</span><br />\n二、為同盟既人建立形象、為敵人建立恐懼既形象、煽動民眾恐慌<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">EG︰建立形象︰小弟理解既就係洗底、普通文宣<br />\n帶動恐慌=抹黑 好似羅范椒芬既free sex論咁</span><br />\n三、準確定位中間選民, 基本有三<br />\n取態猶豫不決的人<br />\n各大五十大版的人<br />\n政治冷感, 不關我的事的人<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">(長輩圖、毛主席圖、講721,831重大革命轉捩點既事件)</span><br />\n四、帶動情緒, exaggerate成功快樂&amp;fail的後果<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">(成功快樂=煲底見/fail=新彊集中營,帶動返巴絲繼續比力抗爭)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>文宣巴絲可以繼續走呢個方向, 幫裝修巴絲洗底, 為手足回血<br />\n岩聽既可以一推<br />\n不岩聽既可以拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"91d68c846610fe780cb9cd951b0bb77506ec690d","tid":1627717,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4816d30dc12a66b742589088d1303c2c54cea2b9","tid":1627717,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"九龍港島見"},{"pid":"5e71790ac7b3c4af2d7529bba37b0e0e49402be8","t